                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250915-182-off965 t18250915-182-cd966"></join>, a feather bed, value 3 l., and a sheet, value 2 s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18250915-182-victim960" type="victimName">
                        Sarah 
                        Cogan
                     <interp inst="t18250915-182-victim960" type="surname" value="Cogan"></interp>
